{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan an Nasai","section":{"1":"The Book of Purification"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":324,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":324}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":187,"arabicnumber":187,"text":"Rapporté par un compagnon : Le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) a bu du lait, puis il a demandé de l’eau, s’est rincé la bouche et a dit : « Il y a de la graisse dedans. »","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":188}}]}